🛒 E-Commerce Analytics Dashboard (SQL + Power BI)
🎯 Business Problem

Analyzed multi-table e-commerce data to identify revenue drivers, customer segmentation, and product performance trends to support data-driven decision making.

🧠 Key Business Questions Solved
Which products and categories drive the highest revenue?
Who are the most valuable customers?
Which cities generate the most sales?
How do customer segments behave over time?
🛠️ Tools & Skills Used
SQL (Joins, Aggregations, Window Functions)
Power BI (Interactive Dashboard, KPI tracking)
Data Modeling (Relational schema design)
Excel (Data validation)
📊 Impact / Insights
Identified Electronics as top revenue-generating category
Found high-value customer segments based on spending behavior
Discovered regional sales concentration (top cities dominate revenue)
Highlighted seasonal revenue fluctuations for business planning
📈 Outcome

Built an interactive dashboard enabling business stakeholders to monitor KPIs and identify growth opportunities across categories and regions.
